                    <div class="service-card">
                        <h3>Cognitive Behavioral Therapy (CBT)</h3>
                        <p>A practical, goal-oriented approach to identify and change negative thought patterns and behaviors contributing to distress.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="service-card">
                        <h3>Trauma Therapy</h3>
                        <p>Specialized support for individuals who have experienced traumatic events, helping to process memories and reduce their emotional impact.</p>
